b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":464,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Issues on Specific Devices in Which the Game Crashes During Raid Battles","message":"<div>We have confirmed an issue in the Resplendent Refrain event, which went live <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1557813600\\"><\/span>, where the game crashes during raid battles on certain devices such as the iPhone 6 and the iPhone 6 Plus that are iOS version 12 or later.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>If you are playing on one of the devices listed above, setting Visual Effects to Basic and Image Quality to Normal in Graphic Settings can mitigate the issue, so please try that.<\/div><div>Follow the steps below to change your settings:<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>1. Tap More on the in-game footer menu.<\/div><div>2. Tap Options.<\/div><div>3. Select the Game tab.<\/div><div>4. Under Graphic Settings, set Visual Effects to Basic, and set Image Quality to Normal.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1557813600,"prev_article_id":"463","next_article_id":"454","image_path":"","update_time":1557739605}}}'